1
00:00:02,790 --> 00:00:05,580
Because of the recipe plagiarism scandal...

2
00:00:05,580 --> 00:00:08,210
The company has been getting...

3
00:00:08,210 --> 00:00:10,500
...a ton of angry phone calls.

4
00:00:10,790 --> 00:00:12,210
I'm so sorry.

5
00:00:12,420 --> 00:00:15,670
And on top of that, at the
10th-anniversary party...

6
00:00:15,670 --> 00:00:17,750
...there were reports of food poisoning.

7
00:00:17,790 --> 00:00:18,710
That's impossible.

8
00:00:18,710 --> 00:00:19,750
I'm extremely careful about food safety.

9
00:00:19,750 --> 00:00:21,920
The person who claimed to have food poisoning...

10
00:00:22,380 --> 00:00:23,710
...was Koda-san.

11
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,080
The woman who only knows how to make bug bait.

12
00:00:25,080 --> 00:00:26,080
Hurry up! Hurry up!

13
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:27,790
If it was her...

14
00:00:28,250 --> 00:00:30,630
She's probably just trying to get revenge.
But if we ignore this...

15
00:00:30,790 --> 00:00:33,880
...it'll blow up into a
huge scandal.

16
00:00:34,080 --> 00:00:35,500
And when that happens...

17
00:00:35,750 --> 00:00:37,380
...your reputation as a culinary expert...

18
00:00:38,000 --> 00:00:39,380
...will go up in smoke.

19
00:00:40,170 --> 00:00:41,130
This is the one thing...

20
00:00:41,130 --> 00:00:42,580
...that absolutely cannot get out.

21
00:00:43,080 --> 00:00:44,580
I don't care what happens to me.

22
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:45,540
If this online exposé makes the news...

23
00:00:45,540 --> 00:00:46,540
...and my father finds out...

24
00:00:46,540 --> 00:00:48,040
...Reika-san will be in serious trouble.

25
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:50,130
You don't want this post...

26
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:51,250
...traced back to you, do you?

27
00:00:51,250 --> 00:00:52,250
No.

28
00:00:52,330 --> 00:00:53,420
That reminds me.

29
00:00:54,330 --> 00:00:56,540
We still haven't settled
that other matter.

30
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:58,000
What other matter?

31
00:00:58,500 --> 00:00:59,500
You know...

32
00:01:00,170 --> 00:01:01,290
The groveling.

33
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,290
If you get on your knees and beg...

34
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:05,040
...I'll stop them from...

35
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,250
...tracing that post back to you.

36
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,290
If this is all it takes
to protect you...

37
00:01:15,710 --> 00:01:17,210
Okay, I'm starting the recording.

38
00:01:18,790 --> 00:01:19,210
Because...

39
00:01:19,420 --> 00:01:21,670
...President Nakama has to
see this.

40
00:01:21,880 --> 00:01:24,290
Who am I apologizing to?

41
00:01:24,330 --> 00:01:26,580
To President Nakama, of course.
For all the trouble you've caused him.

42
00:01:28,170 --> 00:01:29,170
I understand.

43
00:01:30,130 --> 00:01:31,290
Go on.

44
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:35,130
I am truly sorry.

45
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:37,630
Your head is still pretty far...

46
00:01:37,630 --> 00:01:38,630
...from the floor, don't you think?

47
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,880
I am truly sorry.

48
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:44,000
Press your forehead to the floor.

49
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,380
I am truly sorry.

50
00:01:46,420 --> 00:01:47,420
I can't hear you.

51
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,460
I am truly sorry!

52
00:01:51,460 --> 00:01:53,710
I'm going to destroy your happiness.

53
00:01:53,920 --> 00:01:56,080
I'm going to protect your happiness.

54
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:57,420
I have to.

55
00:01:58,580 --> 00:01:59,580
I can't wait to show this video...

56
00:01:59,790 --> 00:02:02,170
...to President Nakama.
I'm so excited.

57
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:04,080
When he sees you like this...

58
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:05,960
...he'll probably...

59
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,540
...dump you on the spot, don't you think?

60
00:02:08,790 --> 00:02:10,080
President Nakama...

61
00:02:10,210 --> 00:02:12,880
...he's handsome and has status.

62
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,420
Someone like you...

63
00:02:14,420 --> 00:02:15,460
...is completely out of his league.

64
00:02:15,830 --> 00:02:18,460
So I think I'll just take him for myself.
